  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Thermador — BSH luxury US brand, Irvine CA parts-chain advantage</h2>
    <p>Thermador is the luxury US positioning brand within BSH Hausgeräte (wholly-owned by Robert Bosch GmbH since 2015). BSH's brand portfolio also includes Bosch (mainstream premium), Gaggenau (ultra-luxury global), and Siemens (European mainstream). Thermador's distinctive position in LA's luxury appliance market is the combination of German BSH engineering lineage with California-resident parts distribution — the BSH Americas HQ operates from Irvine CA, which means Thermador parts for LA service run shorter lead times than Wisconsin-sourced (Sub-Zero Group for Wolf), Tennessee/Mississippi-sourced (Middleby for Viking), or New Jersey-sourced (Miele) luxury brands.</p>
    <p>The Irvine parts-chain advantage is real for service economics — common Thermador parts (bake elements, sensors, control-board sub-variants, door hardware) run 1-2 day lead times through Irvine distribution to LA, versus 3-7 days on comparable luxury brands. We stock common Thermador service parts on the truck for single-visit resolution; specialty Thermador parts (Sapphire Steam boiler elements, current-generation Masterpiece control boards, specific Pro-Series variants) still benefit from Irvine proximity with 2-4 day typical lead.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Thermador wall oven product lines we service</h2>
    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Masterpiece Series 30" / 36" (current flagship)</h3><p>Modern flush-mount integrated-kitchen aesthetic. Updated control platform, refined convection system. Single + double configurations. Service: bake element, convection fan, control board, sensors, door hardware, flush-mount alignment.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Professional Series 30" / 36" (mid-tier)</h3><p>Pro-style design language with commercial-aesthetic handles. Large LA install base from 2010s renovations. Shares many component parts with Masterpiece but different control platform and aesthetic trim.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Sapphire Steam signature steam oven</h3><p>Pure steam + convection in dedicated cavity. Steam boiler + descale cycle + steam-distribution valve. LA hard-water annual descaling cadence. Unique Thermador category, separate from Masterpiece/Professional.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Speed Oven (microwave + convection)</h3><p>Built-in microwave + convection combo. Integrated control panel. Service: magnetron + microwave-side interlocks, convection element + fan, integrated panel electronics.</p></div>
